    "description": "Select CityWalk, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Sales Manager for our Jaipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Select CityWalk:\nSelect CityWalk is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Select CityWalk!",
